00:45:46.950 --> 00:45:47.520
restaurants.

00:45:47.520 --> 00:45:51.680
Can you tell us about some of
the extra things that go into

00:45:51.680 --> 00:45:54.010
your career outside
of cooking?

00:45:54.010 --> 00:45:55.650
ALEX GUARNASCHELLI: Like what?

00:45:55.650 --> 00:45:56.975
Specifically?

00:45:56.975 --> 00:45:59.440
AUDIENCE: Like appearances
at Google.

00:45:59.440 --> 00:46:05.535
Like public appearances,
management, and other aspects

00:46:05.535 --> 00:46:09.030
to being a television
